Subject: Bullets for Kean Presentation
Mime-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=ANSI_X3.4-1968
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 7bit
X-From: Paul Dawson
X-To: Peter Styles, Richard Shapiro
