Bcc: richard.shapiro@enron.com
X-From: Janine Migden
X-To: Scott Gahn, Jeff Ader, Edward D Baughman, James D Steffes, Eric Letke, Harry Kingerski, Marc Ulrich, Charles Decker, James W Lewis, Guy Sharfman, Roy Boston, Susan M Landwehr, Mark Bernstein, Daniel Allegretti, Mike Roan, Scott Stoness, Neil Bresnan, Don Black, Christi L Nicolay, Ron McNamara, Ress Young, Suzanne Rhodes
