From MAILER-DAEMON Mon Apr 18 14:26:42 2022
Message-ID: <21393508.1075844244453.JavaMail.evans@thyme>
Date: Fri, 25 May 2001 04:27:00 -0700 (PDT)
From: larry.decker@enron.com
