West Virginia, Arkansas and Louisiana.
9.  Support EBS in certifications and other issues in the midwest.
10. Support gas asset management deals such as Columbia gas/Nisource and 
manage other gas deals such as  Peoples.
11. Support power plant projects and manage risk on the control areas.

