Date: Thu, 24 May 2001 06:54:00 -0700 (PDT)
From: paul.dawson@enron.com
To: richard.shapiro@enron.com
Subject: FW: Frontier Economics' Whitepaper
Cc: nick.elms@enron.com
Mime-Version: 1.0
