Andrea Calo
06/29/2001 06:49 PM
To: Jose Bestard/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT, Sergio 
Assad/SA/Enron@Enron, Michael Guerriero/SA/Enron@Enron, Remi 
