	steve.walton@enron.com, andy.rodriquez@enron.com
X-From: Charles Yeung
X-To: Kevin M Presto
X-cc: Bill Rust, James D Steffes, Richard Shapiro, Christi L Nicolay, Lloyd Will, Steve Walton, Andy Rodriquez
X-bcc: 
X-Folder: \Richard_Shapiro_June2001\Notes Folders\Discussion threads
