Bcc: gfergus@brobeck.com, richard.b.sanders@enron.com, sbishop@gibbs-bruns.com
X-From: "Dan Watkiss" <dwatkiss@bracepatt.com>
X-To: <jsteffe@enron.com>, <linda.robertson@enron.com>, <ray.alvarez@enron.com>, <rfrank@enron.com>, <Richard.Shapiro@enron.com>, <snovose@enron.com>
X-cc: <gfergus@brobeck.com>, <Richard.B.Sanders@enron.com>, <sbishop@gibbs-bruns.com>
