Jim, I have added responses below in ALL CAPS. 

 Joe Connor


	James D Steffes@EES
	09/20/2000 07:17 PM
		 
		 To: Joe Connor/NA/Enron@Enron, Christi L Nicolay/HOU/ECT@ECT, Tom 
Chapman/HOU/ECT@ECT, Steve Montovano/DUB/EES@EES, Joe 
