Bcc: susan.landwehr@enron.com, richard.shapiro@enron.com
X-From: Janine Migden
X-To: Jeff Ader, Mark Bernstein, Edward D Baughman, Marc Ulrich, Harry Kingerski, James D Steffes, Roy Boston, Daniel Allegretti, Eric Letke, Mike Roan
X-cc: Susan M Landwehr, Richard Shapiro
