From MAILER-DAEMON Mon Apr 18 14:26:43 2022
Message-ID: <25258984.1075852000827.JavaMail.evans@thyme>
Date: Mon, 11 Jun 2001 23:54:00 -0700 (PDT)
From: amr.ibrahim@enron.com
To: richard.shapiro@enron.com
Subject: India - Progress Report One
Cc: james.steffes@enron.com
Mime-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=us-ascii
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 7bit
Bcc: james.steffes@enron.com
X-From: Amr Ibrahim
X-To: Richard Shapiro
